---
/** Grote, eenvoudige CTA-band (design brief §7H, referentiestijl). */
---

<section class="bg-teal-600">
  <div
    class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col items-start gap-6 px-6 py-12 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between md:py-14"
  >
    <div class="reveal flex items-start gap-5 md:items-center">
      <span
        class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/15 p-3 text-white"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        <svg
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="1.8"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
        >
          <rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="16" rx="2"></rect>
          <path d="M8 3v4m8-4v4M3 10h18"></path>
          <path d="m9.5 15.5 2 2 3.5-4"></path>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <div>
        <h2
          class="font-display text-[22px] font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight text-white md:text-[26px]"
        >
          Een sterk netwerk begint met een goed gesprek.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-1.5 max-w-xl text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-teal-50/90">
          Vertel ons over uw gebouw. Wij zorgen voor de rest.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal shrink-0">
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-[15px] font-medium text-teal-600 transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-teal-50"
      >
        Plan een vrijblijvend gesprek
        <span
          class="transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-[3px]"
          aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span
        >
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
